{"tid":523842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"同事爆料繼母酷刑打兄妹 打斷籐條 膠紙封口","createTime":"2018-01-09T03:44:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T07:18:27.000Z","uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5c23dbddfe3ade0b1065be1a68932c2bf3b1f5cc","tid":523842,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T03:44:09.000Z","msg":"同事爆料繼母酷刑打兄妹 打斷籐條 膠紙封口<br />\n<br />\n屯門時代廣場5歲女童臨臨被虐待致死案件，據知臨臨父母原是中學同學，但因繼母介入引發三角戀最終婚變，其父年前與繼母再婚，之後有人拒絕臨臨和兄長與生母見面。去年年尾，臨臨與哥哥的生活墮入地獄，不但被人用籐條抽打、罰跪，還要用膠紙封口，懲罰她「唔肯講嘢」。<br />\n<br />\n據知情人士向《蘋果》表示，臨臨的繼母於去年曾在屯門一間連鎖藥店集團當售貨員，其間多次向同事透露虐兒經過，每次都說得眉飛色舞，毫無悔意。有同事憶述「佢話仔女唔聽話，要打」，更指除用藤條體罰，還罰子女跪地思過；由於子女頑皮，連藤條亦打斷。她又稱丈夫跟前妻的幼女有語言障礙「唔肯講嘢，要用封箱膠紙封佢個嘴，唔俾佢講嘢！」"},{"pid":"57c059fdf6c934117868547bed6d279578d84e04","tid":523842,"uid":50719,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T03:47:11.000Z","msg":"咁個同事唔報警！？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/as